CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 18, 1967, pg. 13 reads: "Founders' Luncheon - Seated around the luncheon table at Stouffers at the AKA Founders' Day event are Sorors Claudia Harper, Maria Oliver, Della Burt, Alma Thomas Burgess, Patricia English, Jewel Garrison, Janet Thompson, Doris Garrison, Dorothy Hendricks, Harriett McCrae, Mary Hall Page, Judith E. Nelson and Yvonne Burnett."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of fourteen Alpha Kappa Alpha members, including Claudia Harper, Maria Oliver, Della Burt, Alma Thomas Burgess, Patricia English, Jewel Garrison, Janet Thompson, Doris Garrison, Dorothy Hendricks, Harriett McCrae, Mary Hall Page, Judith E. Nelson, and Yvonne Burnett gathered at rectangular table in Stouffers Restaurant during Founders Day celebration
